---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
const pageTitle = 'Privacy Policy - Alexis Fiska';
const pageDescription =
  'This policy explains how your data is collected and used when you use the website and the contact form.';
---
<BaseLayout lang={lang} title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <p>
      This website does not collect personal data beyond the information you choose to provide via the contact form.
      Data submitted through this form is processed by the Formspree service. It is used solely to respond to your
      request and retained only for as long as needed for follow-up. You may request deletion of this information
      at any time by writing to <a href="mailto:alexissfiska@gmail.com">alexissfiska@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      For analytics, we use <strong>Plausible Analytics</strong>, a privacy-friendly solution that sets no cookies and
      does not collect personally identifiable data. Only anonymized statistics are recorded (page views,
      referrers, etc.).
    </p>
    <p>
      In accordance with the GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, and delete your data. To exercise these rights
      or ask a question about this privacy policy, please contact us by email.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
